  "title": "Part Time Contact Centre Agent ($80-$120/day)",
  "description": "<p>Upnon Academy is a financial literacy academy formed with the mission of fulfilling dreams for working adults and underprivileged children through financial education without money worries.  </p><p>To achieve this, we seek driven individuals with integrity to join us.<br /><br /><strong>About the Role:</strong></p><p>Join our Call Centre team to be the first point of contact for our organization. You will be responsible for professionally handling a high volume of inbound and outbound calls.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>· Manage inbound and outbound communications (calls) promptly and in accordance with our policies</p><p>· Maintain strict confidentiality of all caller information</p><p>· Route calls and inquiries accurately to the appropriate internal departments</p><p>· Accurately update contact details and information within the Call Centre System</p><p>· Address and resolve customer complaints with empathy and efficiency</p><p>· Report any faults with telecommunications equipment</p><p>· Perform other related duties as assigned</p><p><strong>Why Join Us:</strong></p><p>. A Part Time role doing meaningful work</p><p>. Daily Rate: $80 to $120</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>. Singaporean Citizen or Singapore Permanent Resident</p><p>. Flexible hours and work schedule: 3 to 7 hours/day, 3 to 5 weekdays/week, 9 to 35 hours/week</p><p>. Work in office Near Queensway Shopping Centre</p><p>· NITEC or equivalent in any discipline. A Diploma will be recognized for senior positions</p><p>· Excellent verbal and written communication skills</p><p>· Proficiency in Microsoft Office Suite (Word, Excel)</p><p>· Willingness to work a rotating shift schedule</p><p>. Share our goal and values</p><p>. Driven individuals with integrity</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Progression:</strong></p><p>Progression to full-time roles</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Application Process:</strong></p><p>If you are looking for a part time role and doing something meaningful, please send us your latest resume</p>",
